            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指開報26394點，跌68點，較上日現貨收市價26487點低水94點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月科指期貨開報5644點，跌30點，低水39點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月國指期貨開報9046點，跌42點，低水49點。</p>\n</div>",
